{
  "text": "Although there have been some studies on sustainable supply networks, many are theoretical, exploratory or normative in nature [CITATION_1] Davis 2007, Carter and [CITATION_2] . There is a continuing need to complement these with further empirical evidence of practice. This paper presents such a study of collaborative supply networks in the international clothing industry.",
